Excel Sales Data Analysis Dashboard

Project Description
Excel Sales Data Analysis project using a self-created dataset. Performed data cleaning, duplicate handling, pivot table analysis, and built a dashboard to derive insights on customers, regions, and products.


Tasks Performed
- Data cleaning and duplicate removal
- Handling repeated customer data
- Created calculated column (Total Sales)
- Built Pivot Tables
- Developed charts (Customer, Region, Product)
- Designed dashboard for insights

##  Key Insights
- Identified top-performing customers
- Analyzed region-wise sales performance
- Found best-selling products
- Compared new vs repeated customers


##  Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
